metadata.name: Little goblin
metadata.description:
The desert thorns never grow up in any place of this planet if there were no little goblins,
There's a myth which say's the goblins always flyblow in deserts & bleed some drops on sands as a sign of their custody over the eggs or in a better term, the little ones which going to born soon.
so in this way ,they never lose their beloved kids.
But thier blood have an effect over the deserts, it becomes the reason of growing thorns all over the sands of deserts & because of that , thorns are dry & withered.

If you listen carefully at night, you'll hear the voice of baby goblins through the thorns...
